.SH "NAME"
Search::Elasticsearch::Client::7_0::Direct::Watcher \- Plugin providing Watcher API for Search::Elasticsearch 7.x
.SH "VERSION"
.IX Header "VERSION"
version 7.30
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
